imdb.plot outline: A deeper journey into the crucial, fragile, interdependence between animal life and the environment. Guided by the most up to date research we travel through jungles, forests, mountain ranges, deserts, and oceans to discover animals, their habitats and the environment that sustains them. Their behavior, ability to develop, survive and adapt to a changing environment is evident.
